node.text:
Todd from @customupfits has such a big heart. He built this awesome custom trailer and donated to help raise money for our friend @brianmoreau104 
To enter, simply buy a 10$ Brian Moreau sticker plate on @customupfits website. It will automatically enter for a chance to win this trailer ! Who wouldn’t want to be going to the races in style ! 
It has a couch, indoor/outdoor Tv, slide out tool box, fridge, locker, LED Light, outdoor shower, sound system... and a super rad electric awning ! Hurry and get your sticker plate today ! Buy more than one sticker plate to increase your chances, that will help @brianmoreau104 A LOT !

node.text:
A little clip of our experience of the @wflworldrun by @wingsforlife I obviously couldn’t run it, but I got to walk 4km before to jump on my road bike and meeting my wife @cmmathilde on her run, and cheer on her ! Proud of her for running 18,8km in 1h46 for THOSE YOU CAN’T ! #KTMworthit
It was fun and we will do it again next year ! Good job to everyone running in my team you guys are amazing ! And sorry for the mix of French and English, but you know what..?! That’s who we are ! 😅@redbull @redbullfrance @ktmusa

node.text:
#KTMworthit I haven't seen this clip since probably the moment it happened. So when my friend sent it to me last week, first I kinda got emotional watching it and  then I thought it would be perfect to share with you for our #KTMworthit moment with @ktmusa
I love these people ! KTM Family ! I can't believe it was already 10 years ago ! Baby Faces Yayyyyy !

node.title: We do what we do to live THESE moments !!

node.text:
PALA MX - 8th and 7th for 7th overall - 
First race is in the books and we’ve seen positive this weekend. Unfortunately a few get off the track cost me time and positions in the first laps of both motos. I tried my best to come back. ➡️ Moving on to Colorado next weekend !

node.text:
Salt Lake City - P.2 | What a night for our team @ktmusa !
It was great to go 1-2 for the team and finish the season on a strong note. It’s been a rough one but we never gave up and made it back to the front and that’s what I will remember of this season. Congrats to my teammate for getting the title. Very impressive. 
Now it’s time to focus on the great Outdoors !
